			</DialogueOption>
		</DialogueOptionsList>
		<SetCondition>SCIENTIST_1</SetCondition>
		<ConditionToCancel>RH_SLATE_FIRE_DAMAGED_RECENT</ConditionToCancel>
		<SetCondition>RH_SLATE_FIRE_DIALOGUE_THISLOOP</SetCondition>
	</DialogueNode>
	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_Fire_TalkToAgain</Name>
		<EntryCondition>RH_SLATE_FIRE_DAMAGED_RECENT</EntryCondition>
		<EntryCondition>SCIENTIST_1</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			<Page>Whoa there, hatchling! Be careful around that fire.</Page>
			<Page>What are you still doing here? Not having second thoughts, are you?</Page>
		</Dialogue>
		<DialogueOptionsList>
			<DialogueOption>
				<Text>Where are the launch codes again?</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswer21</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
				<Text>How’s the ship looking?</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswer22</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
				<Text>How safe would you say this thing is?</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswer23</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
				<Text>What’s my mission once I’m in space?</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswer24</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
				<Text>What else should I do before liftoff?</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswer25</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
		</DialogueOptionsList>
		<ConditionToCancel>RH_SLATE_FIRE_DAMAGED_RECENT</ConditionToCancel>
		<SetCondition>RH_SLATE_FIRE_DIALOGUE_THISLOOP</SetCondition>
	</DialogueNode>
	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_Fire_L3</Name>
		<EntryCondition>RH_SLATE_FIRE_DAMAGED_RECENT</EntryCondition>
		<EntryCondition>LOOP_COUNT_GOE_3</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			<Page>Whoa there, hatchling! Be careful around that fire.</Page>
			<Page>Ready to get this thing off the ground?</Page>
		</Dialogue>
		<DialogueOptionsList>
			<DialogueOption>
				<Text>You know the ship is a death-trap, right?</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswer35</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
				<Text>You’re lucky I’m in a time loop, because otherwise I’d be super dead.</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswer36</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
				<RequiredPersistentCondition>AUTOPILOT_INTO_SUN</RequiredPersistentCondition>
				<Text>The autopilot flew my ship directly into the sun!</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswer37</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
				<RequiredPersistentCondition>KILLED_IN_GHOST_MATTER</RequiredPersistentCondition>
				<Text>I keep getting killed by ghost matter.</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswer38</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
				<RequiredPersistentCondition>KILLED_BY_SUPERNOVA_AND_KNOWS_IT</RequiredPersistentCondition>
				<Text>The sun is going to go supernova, by the way.</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswer39</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
				<RequiredPersistentCondition>THERE_IS_BUT_VOID</RequiredPersistentCondition>
				<Text>Did you know it’s just an endless void outside our solar system?</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswer40</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
		</DialogueOptionsList>
		<ConditionToCancel>RH_SLATE_FIRE_DAMAGED_RECENT</ConditionToCancel>
		<SetCondition>RH_SLATE_FIRE_DIALOGUE_THISLOOP</SetCondition>
	</DialogueNode>

	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>ScientistSpace</Name>
		<EntryCondition>Space</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			<Page>Oh! Hatchling, what're you doing back here so soon? Get back up there and have some fun!</Page>
			<Page>Don't tell me you're getting cold feet now… come on, it's perfectly safe, swear on my top eyes.</Page>
		</Dialogue>
	</DialogueNode>
	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_Space_Fire</Name>
		<EntryCondition>RH_SLATE_FIRE_DAMAGED_RECENT</EntryCondition>
		<EntryCondition>Space</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			<Page>Whoa there, hatchling! Be careful around that fire.</Page>
			<Page>What are you doing back here? Don't tell me you're getting cold feet. Or, uhh… warm feet, I suppose.</Page>
			<Page>The ship's perfectly safe, hatchling. Swear on my top eyes.</Page>
		</Dialogue>
		<ConditionToCancel>RH_SLATE_FIRE_DAMAGED_RECENT</ConditionToCancel>
		<SetCondition>RH_SLATE_FIRE_DIALOGUE_THISLOOP</SetCondition>
	</DialogueNode>
	
	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_CoolThing</Name>
		<EntryCondition>RH_COOLTHINGHELD</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			<Page>Whoa! What's that you got there, hatchling? Looks mighty interesting to me.</Page>
			<Page>I have no idea what it is, though. Maybe run it by Hornfels if you're curious.</Page>
		</Dialogue>
	</DialogueNode>
	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_RedSun_Prior</Name>
		<EntryCondition>RH_REDSUN</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			<Page>…Hey, hatchling. Is it just me, or was the sun looking kind of red earlier?</Page>
		</Dialogue>
		<DialogueOptionsList>
			<DialogueOption>
				<RequiredPersistentCondition>KILLED_BY_SUPERNOVA_AND_KNOWS_IT</RequiredPersistentCondition>
				<Text>It's about to go supernova.</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswerRH1</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
				<Text>Was it? I haven't noticed.</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswerRH2</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
		</DialogueOptionsList>
	</DialogueNode>
	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_RedSun_Overhead</Name>
		<EntryCondition>RH_REDSUN</EntryCondition>
		<EntryCondition>RH_VILLAGEDAY</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			<Page>Jeez… sun's looking kinda red, isn't it?</Page>
		</Dialogue>
		<DialogueOptionsList>
			<DialogueOption>
				<RequiredPersistentCondition>KILLED_BY_SUPERNOVA_AND_KNOWS_IT</RequiredPersistentCondition>
				<Text>It's about to go supernova.</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswerRH1</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
				<Text>Is it? I haven't noticed.</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswerRH2</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
		</DialogueOptionsList>
	</DialogueNode>
	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_TellHornfels</Name>
		<EntryCondition>SCIENTIST_RH_SNTELLHORNFELS</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			<Page>…Did you tell Hornfels yet?</Page>
		</Dialogue>
		<DialogueOptionsList>
			<DialogueOption>
				<RequiredCondition>HORNFELS_RH_SUPERNOVADENY</RequiredCondition>
				<Text>Yeah, they think you're going crazy.</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswerRH3</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
			<DialogueOption>
					<Text>No, not yet.</Text>
				<DialogueTarget>ScientistAnswerRH4</DialogueTarget>
			</DialogueOption>
		</DialogueOptionsList>
	</DialogueNode>
