	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_HornfellsResolved_Space</Name>
		<EntryCondition>SCIENTIST_RH_HORNFELLSRESOLVED</EntryCondition>
		<EntryCondition>Space</EntryCondition>
		<DialogueTarget>ScientistSpace</DialogueTarget>
	</DialogueNode>
	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_Distraught</Name>
		<EntryCondition>SCIENTIST_RH_DISTRAUGHT</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			 <Page>No, no… it couldn't be. Chert would've seen it coming… right?</Page>
		</Dialogue>
	</DialogueNode>
	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_Boom</Name>
		<EntryCondition>RH_BOOM</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			<Page>…Oh.</Page>
			<Page>Hatchling… I don't think we have much time left.</Page>
			<Page>Just… sit here by the fire with me, okay? It'll be alright.</Page>
		</Dialogue>
		<SetCondition>SCIENTIST_RH_SILENT</SetCondition>
	</DialogueNode>
	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_BoomDistraught</Name>
		<EntryCondition>RH_BOOM</EntryCondition>
		<EntryCondition>SCIENTIST_RH_DISTRAUGHT</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			<Page>Gah! Oh, hatchling, you were right. You were right… why?!</Page>
			<Page>It's… it's fine. It'll be fine, just… just sit here by the fire with me, okay? It'll be alright.</Page>
		</Dialogue>
		<SetCondition>SCIENTIST_RH_SILENT</SetCondition>
	</DialogueNode>
	<DialogueNode>
		<Name>Scientist_RH_Silent</Name>
		<EntryCondition>SCIENTIST_RH_SILENT</EntryCondition>
		<Dialogue>
			<Page>…Close your eyes, hatchling.</Page>
		</Dialogue>
	</DialogueNode>
